# API Design: AI-Powered Appraisal System

## API Overview

| Property | Decision |
|----------|----------|
| **Architecture Style** | RESTful |
| **Protocol** | HTTPS |
| **Data Format** | JSON (application/json) |
| **Base URL** | `https://api.mycompany.com/v1` |
| **Documentation Standard** | OpenAPI 3.0+ |

## Authentication & Authorization

### Authentication Method

| Method | Details |
|--------|---------|
| **Scheme** | JWT (JSON Web Tokens) |
| **Header** | `Authorization: Bearer <token>` |
| **Token Lifetime** | Access: 15 minutes, Refresh: 7 days |
| **Storage** | HTTP-only cookie or Secure LocalStorage |

### Authorization Flow
┌──────────┐ ┌──────────┐ ┌──────────┐
│ Client │────▶│ /login │────▶│ Auth │
│ │◀────│ │◀────│ Server │
└──────────┘ └──────────┘ └──────────┘
│ │ │
│ JWT Token │ │
│◀────────────────┘ │
│ │
│ Request + Bearer Token │
│────────────────────────────────────▶│
│ │
│ Role-based Access Control (RBAC) │
│◀────────────────────────────────────│

text

### Role-Based Access Control (RBAC)

| Role | Permission Level | Accessible Resources |
|------|-----------------|---------------------|
| **employee** | Read own data, write context/achievements | `/api/employee/*` |
| **manager** | Read/write team data, appraisals | `/api/manager/*`, `/api/employee/*` (team only) |
| **hr** | Full read/write on calibration, audit, compliance | `/api/hr/*`, `/api/manager/*`, `/api/employee/*` |
| **admin** | System configuration, integrations, cycles | `/api/admin/*`, all others |
| **leader** | Read-only org summaries | `/api/leader/*` |

### Permission Matrix

| Endpoint Group | employee | manager | hr | admin | leader |
|----------------|----------|---------|----|-------|--------|
| `/api/auth/*` | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ |
| `/api/employee/*` | ✓ (own) | ✓ (team) | ✓ (all) | ✓ | ✗ |
| `/api/manager/*` | ✗ | ✓ | ✓ | ✓ | ✗ |
| `/api/hr/*` | ✗ | ✗ | ✓ | ✓ | ✗ |
| `/api/leader/*` | ✗ | ✗ | ✗ | ✗ | ✓ |
| `/api/admin/*` | ✗ | ✗ | ✗ | ✓ | ✗ |

