## API Endpoints

### 1. Authentication & User Context

| Method | Endpoint | Description | Auth |
|--------|----------|-------------|------|
| `POST` | `/api/auth/login` | Email/password login; returns user profile, role, JWT token | Public |
| `POST` | `/api/auth/logout` | Blacklist token and invalidate session | Required |
| `GET` | `/api/auth/me` | Get current user’s role, team ID, permissions | Required |
| `POST` | `/api/auth/refresh` | Refresh expired JWT token | Required |
| `POST` | `/api/auth/change-password` | Change user password | Required |

