Versioning Strategy
Versioning Method
Decision	Value
Method	URL path prefix
Format	/v1/, /v2/
Deprecation Policy	12 months notice
Deprecation Header	Deprecation: true
Version Lifecycle
text
┌─────────┐     ┌─────────┐     ┌─────────┐     ┌─────────┐
│ Current │────▶│   Beta  │────▶│  Stable │────▶│Deprecated│
│  (v1)   │     │  (v2)   │     │  (v2)   │     │  (v1)   │
└─────────┘     └─────────┘     └─────────┘     └─────────┘
     │               │               │               │
     │               │               │               │
     ▼               ▼               ▼               ▼
  Production      Early           Full              Sunset
   Only           Adopters        Release           (12 months)
Version Headers
Header	Value	Description
API-Version	2026-05-01	Date-based version
Deprecation	true	Marks deprecated endpoints
Sunset	Mon, 01 May 2027 00:00:00 GMT	Sunset date
Breaking vs Non-Breaking Changes
Change Type	Version Bump	Example
Add new endpoint	Minor (v1.1)	New /metrics endpoint
Add optional field	Minor	New avatar_url field
Remove field	Major (v2.0)	Remove deprecated old_field
Change field type	Major	id from number to string
Change required field	Major	Make email required
