API Call Summary by Role
Role	Primary Endpoint Group	Key Operations
Employee	/api/employee/*	View dashboard, add context, submit achievements, upload artifacts
Manager	/api/manager/*	View team, generate/override AI drafts, calibrate, approve appraisals
